import sys

k, x = map(int, sys.stdin.readline().split())

for i in range(max(x - k + 1, -1000000), min(x + k, 1000000) + 1):
    print(i, end=" ")


import sys

k, x = list(map(int, sys.stdin.readline().split()))

for i in range(k):
    print(x - k + 1 + i, end=" ")
